title: Dianne Feinstein - Wikipedia
snippet: Dianne Emiel Feinstein (née Goldman; June 22, 1933 – September 29, 2023) was an American politician who served as a United States senator from California from 1992 until her death in 2023.

title: Biography - United States Senator for California
snippet: A native of San Francisco, Senator Feinstein served for nine years as a San Francisco County Supervisor, starting in 1969.
